   on PageSpeed Insights performance tests.

Loads in Less than 1 Second

   We’ve made speed our top priority to make sure your site runs fast. On
   a default install, Neve took 0.6s to load.

Reduced Weight

   We’ve created a lightweight theme without sacrificing flexibility.
   Total default WordPress install is as tiny as 28KB.
