Everything a Theme Should Be (And Much More)

   Translation & RTL Ready Translation & RTL Ready

Translation & RTL Ready

   So you’re building a website that might not be written in English? No
   problem. Every element in this theme can be translated with free and
   premium plugins. Plus, you can use any RTL language.
   SEO Friendly﻿ SEO Friendly﻿

SEO Friendly Markup

   Search Engine Optimization is a must these days if you want your
   business to have a strong online presence.
   Google will love your site because of the SEO-ready structure, plus a
   clean and optimized source code.
   [theme-icon3-neve.svg] [theme-icon3-neve.svg]

No jQuery

   Neve uses Vanilla JavaScript for performance optimization. Because No
   jQuery is loaded, render blocking issues should be a thing of the past.
   The theme is fast and lightweight without jQuery.
   1-Minute Setup & Demo import 1-Minute Setup & Demo import

Fast and Easy Onboarding

   Long story short, what this basically means is that, with this theme,
   you can import a ready-made website in less than 5 minutes. No joke.
   Custom Backgrounds Custom Backgrounds

Easily Customizable

   A fast and lightweight theme that lets you do all. Just set up your
   website and start customizing each element. No extra work required.
   Optimized for speed﻿ Optimized for speed﻿

Optimized for Speed

   This theme gives you all: compatibility with popular caching and
   minification plugins, not to mention the ultra fast loading times that
   you get right out the box.
   Mega Menus Mega Menus

1-Click Rollback

   The option to go back to the previous version is available with all our
   products. The most common reason to use the rollback feature is to
   “reverse” an update that didn’t go so well.
   1-Click Updates & Fast Support 1-Click Updates & Fast Support

Safe Updates & Fast Support

   We detect breaking changes in theme updates before we push them.
   Eyepatch is the service that provides reliable visual regression
   assistance to help detect and avoid breaking changes.
   Video Tutorials Video Tutorials

Accessibility Ready

   Optimizing for accessibility is essential. We made Neve user-friendly
   for those with special challenges. Besides simply being the right thing
   to do, this will ensure anyone can interact with your content.

